title: Starting The New Year with Healthy Habits
description:
It's that time of year again... when everyone you know commits to becoming healthier, more efficient, more present, more [insert your adjective here]. The only problem is that "New Year, New Me" mentally doesn't usually stick. So Judah and Chelsea are here to share their best tips and tricks about how to form new healthy habits and ultimately create lasting change in your life.
